            "email": "ablazajrtc@gmail.com",
            "position": null,
            "office": "Johanna Research and Training Center",
            "content": "<p><small>The Johanna Research and Training Center caters to students, professional scholars, youth, government officials, leaders and community. The center&rsquo;s areas of concerns are research, training, board review and social services.</small><p><strong>POTENTIAL CONTRIBUTION TO THE NETWORK:</strong></p><ul>\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t<ul>\r\n\t\t<li>\r\n\t\t<p>Develop and enhance the culture of research within the students and young professionals within the region.</p>\r\n\t\t</li>\r\n\t\t<li>\r\n\t\t<p>Conduct necessary training and quality researches that has influence to the Asian and international community.</p>\r\n\t\t</li>\r\n\t\t<li>\r\n\t\t<p>Initiate and conduct researches and training that will directly benefit the life Filipino people.</p>\r\n\t\t</li>\r\n\t\t<li>\r\n\t\t<p>Utilize research and training as a tool in promoting inclusive development learning and preserving the rich culture of the Filipino people.</p>\r\n\t\t</li>\r\n\t\t<li>\r\n\t\t<p>Provide training and technical assistance to students and local researchers.</p>\r\n\t\t</li>\r\n\t</ul>\r\n\t</li>\r\n</ul><p><strong>INSTITUTIONAL DEVELOPMENT AND CAPACITY BUILDING SERVICES:</strong></p><ul>\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t<p>Conduct of capacity building on qualitative research through a series of training workshop on qualitative research in the City of Palawan and Baguio.</p>\r\n\t</li>\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t<p>Conduct of Training on how to productively perform duties and responsibilities as newly elected officials in the government. (Both Barangay and SK officials)</p>\r\n\t</li>\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t<p>Provision of Continuing Professional Development to teachers and criminologist.</p>\r\n\t</li>\r\n</ul><p><strong>AVAILABLE RESOURCES (that can be shared to the network)</strong></p><ul>\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t<ul>\r\n\t\t<li>\r\n\t\t<p>Human resource &ndash; we can share our expertise in line with our organizational operations, we can share our knowledge and skills regarding training, researches and the different expertise of our member in their different professions.</p>\r\n\t\t</li>\r\n\t</ul>\r\n\t</li>\r\n</ul></p>\n",
